Easy access to Suburban Collection Showplace

Find our hotel off I-96, within half-a-mile of restaurants and shops in Novi. Twelve Oaks Mall and events at Suburban Collection Showplace are within two miles. Downtown Detroit can be reached in 30 minutes. We have an indoor pool, 24-business center, and a free local shuttle service. Enjoy a warm DoubleTree cookie on arrival.

Cancellation

Cancellation policies may vary depending on the rate and dates of your reservation. Please refer to your reservation confirmation to verify your cancellation policy. If you need further assistance, call the hotel directly or contact customer service. Alternatively, you can cancel your reservation online.

Face Coverings

We ask that you follow all local guidelines and laws with respect to practicing social distancing and wearing a mask in public areas. Please check with local public health and government authorities regarding guidelines or requirements that may be in place for the location of your stay.

Housekeeping: Tailored To Your Comfort

Stayover housekeeping service is complimentary and available upon request during your stay. Simply contact the front desk at any time to request extra towels and amenities or to schedule a room cleaning. For stays of four (4) nights or more, we will provide full cleaning every fourth night/fifth day for all guests.
